================================================================================
Third-party components and model weights
================================================================================

lerobot-curate does NOT bundle any model weights or third-party source code in
its source tree, sdist, or wheel. The components below are pulled at install
time (Python dependencies) or downloaded on first use (model weights). Each
retains its own license.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Model weights (downloaded on first use via huggingface_hub; NEVER bundled)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Default embedder: Xenova/siglip-base-patch16-224 (ONNX, int8)
    The Xenova ONNX repackaging is a conversion of google/siglip-base-patch16-224.
    Upstream google/siglip is released under the Apache License 2.0:
        https://huggingface.co/google/siglip-base-patch16-224
    Weights are fetched to the local Hugging Face cache on first use and are
    never committed to git nor included in any distributed artifact of this
    project. If you do not run the real embedder, no weights are downloaded.
    Fallback under evaluation for v0.1.1: onnx-community/siglip2-base-patch16-224.

