--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Method attribution (algorithms re-implemented from published papers)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The embedding dedup / suboptimal-detection approach is a CPU reference
re-implementation inspired by SCIZOR (arXiv:2505.22626). The signature-kernel
trajectory-diversity approach is a CPU reference re-implementation inspired by
FAKTUAL (arXiv:2603.11634). This project does NOT reproduce the policy-learning
performance numbers reported in those papers (which require GPU policy training
and are out of scope). See README.md for the full scope disclaimer.
